            <h1>Welcome to Esalona</h1>
            <p>For reasons known only to yourself, you're in the city of Esalona on the continent of <a href="world.php">Seishun</a>. Depending on where you're from, you may feel out of place amongst all the fine robes and streets so clean it almost feels like a crime to walk on them.</p> 
            <p>Yet anyone who's stepped foot outside the great walls surrounding it knows even a city like this has its problems. Most of Seishun is a harsh, untamed wilderness where strange forces have been known to swallow settlements whole and many who step foot outside never return. For this reason the lot of an adventurer is a dangerous one, but also one both sorely needed and well rewarded.</p>
