            <h2>Technology</h2>
            <p>Regardless of where you came from, you've likely noticed rooms tend to be lit by small contained fires and other objects that naturally emit light. Traveling merchants go from place to place in horse drawn carriages, which are almost always guarded by a group of skilled mercenaries or bodyguards. </p>
            <p>Yet while this is a world of swords and magic, most people have heard of the magitech guns from Drechen. These weapons tend to be very expensive due to their rare, exotic nature and you're unlikely to find someone capable of working with them in Seishun.</p>
            <p>It is worth noting that magitech is illegal in Akalush, but you're unlikely to run into problems for using it in Seishun.</p>

