            <h2>Places of Note</h2>
            <p>As an adventurer, there are a few places you're likely already aware of.</p>
            <p><b>The Heroes Guild: </b>Their primary purpose is to act as a go between for adventurers and their clients, though they also try to keep adventurers informed of known dangers outside the city.</p>
            <p><b>Greensong Tavern: </b>A large, popular tavern that's hard to miss if you've been in the city long enough. Not a bad place to gather information or grab a room for a night.</p>
            <p><b>Temple of Truth: </b>A temple dedicated to <a href="religions.php">Nessthiss</a>. Because it attracts a lot of scholarly types hoping to learn the secrets of the world, it's not unusual for them to hire adventurers.</p>
            
